dist

# Lockfile intentionally untracked: npm's cross-platform optional-dependency
# handling for esbuild produces lockfiles that fail `npm ci` on Cloudflare's
# linux/x64 builders. Without a lockfile, the builder runs `npm install`, which
# resolves natively and skips non-matching platform packages.
package-lock.json
dist-ssr
*.local
.DS_Store
.vite
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
